                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7334" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1829</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8447 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">突围之路——A电视购物公司如何实现逆风翻盘？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The way to break through -- How does A TV shopping company realize reverse wind?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张晓明，钟丽珍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A电视购物公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电视购物公司；战略转型；传统媒体</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TV shopping company; Strategic transformation；Traditional media</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在互联网高度发达的今天，传统媒体优势不再，电视的黄金时代似乎已经接近尾声，而电视购物作为以电视为载体的媒体零售行业，在中国已经经历了30年的起起伏伏，慢慢也沦为人们眼中的夕阳产业。现阶段，媒体融合向纵深发展，电商直播风头正劲，在行业整体发展转型的“十字路口”，各个电视购物频道纷纷寻求新的“破圈突围”之路。尤其是近几年，受电视开机率逐年下滑影响，电视购物的用户流失严重，行业内同质化竞争加剧，发展变得异常艰难，急需寻找自己的突破口，A公司正是目前电视购物行业中面临转型困惑的一员。本案例引导学生聚焦于战略转型的问题研究，启迪学生系统的分析和认识战略转型的相关问题，进而提升对于战略转型的管理能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In today&#39;s highly developed Internet, the advantages of traditional media are no longer, the golden age of television seems to have come to an end, and TV shopping, as a media retail industry based on television, has experienced 30 years of ups and downs in China, and has gradually become a sunset industry in people&#39;s eyes. At this stage, media convergence is developing in depth, and e-commerce live broadcasting is gaining momentum. At the &quot;crossroads&quot; of the overall development and transformation of the industry, various TV shopping channels are seeking new ways to &quot;break through the circle&quot;. Especially in recent years, affected by the decline of TV opening rate year by year, the loss of TV shopping users is serious, the homogenization competition in the industry is intensified, the development has become extremely difficult, and it is urgent to find their own breakthrough, A company is one of the current TV shopping industry facing transition confusion. This case guides students to focus on the study of strategic transformation issues, enlighten students to systematically analyze and understand the issues related to strategic transformation, so as to improve the management ability of strategic transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PEST分析法；战略转型含义和理论；SWOT分析法战略转型的方向；核心竞争力多元化转型；核心竞争力差异化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
